						<div class="col-xl-12 col-lg-12" data-aos="fade-left">
							<h3 class="faq-title">Use Cases of NLP</h3>
							<div class="accordion accordion-style-one" id="accordionOne">
								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
										<button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
											data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false"
											aria-controls="collapseOne">
											Sentiment Analysis
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
										aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP can be used to analyze text data from sources such as social media,
												customer reviews, and surveys to determine the sentiment or opinion
												expressed towards a particular topic, product, or service. This
												information is valuable for businesses to understand customer feedback,
												assess brand reputation, and make informed decisions.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
										<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
											data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
											aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
											Text Classification
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
										aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP algorithms can classify text documents into predefined categories or
												topics based on their content. This is useful for tasks such as document
												categorization, spam detection, news categorization, and content tagging
												in content management systems.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
										<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
											data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
											aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
											Named Entity Recognition (NER)
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
										aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP techniques can identify and extract named entities, such as people,
												organizations, locations, dates, and numerical expressions, from
												unstructured text data. NER is commonly used in applications like
												information extraction, entity linking, and document summarization.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
										<button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
											data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="true"
											aria-controls="collapseFour">
											Machine Translation
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
										aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP plays a crucial role in machine translation systems that
												automatically translate text from one language to another. These systems
												use advanced statistical and neural machine translation models to
												accurately translate text while preserving its meaning and context.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
										<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
											data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive"
											aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
											Question Answering Systems
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
										aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP algorithms can power question answering systems that understand and
												respond to user queries in natural language. These systems can retrieve
												relevant information from large knowledge bases or textual corpora to
												provide accurate and contextually relevant answers to user questions.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
										<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
											data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix"
											aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
											Chatbots and Virtual Assistants
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading"
										data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP is the backbone of chatbots and virtual assistants that interact with
												users through natural language conversations. These systems use
												techniques like natural language understanding (NLU) and natural
												language generation (NLG) to understand user queries, perform tasks, and
												generate human-like responses.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="accordion-item">
									<div class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven">
										<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
											data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSeven"
											aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
											Text Summarization
										</button>
									</div>
									<div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
										aria-labelledby="headingSeven" data-bs-parent="#accordionOne">
										<div class="accordion-body">
											<p>NLP algorithms can automatically generate concise summaries of longer
												text documents or articles, capturing the key points and main ideas
												while omitting redundant or irrelevant information. Text summarization
												is useful for tasks such as document summarization, news summarization,
												and content curation.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
